item.title: Here I go PyGrunn'13!
item.description: I am really proud of say that the next month I will be giving a talk at PyGrunn! This is a really good new for me because PyGrunn is the conference that my old colleagues organize since years ago. I was on it first time in 2011 just one week after I started working at Paylogic. I meet a lot of interesting people there and I will see them again this year!
